[u][b]English[/b][/u]
Keeping the truth of her past unseen, Aleysha will play the part of a princess and be offered in sacrifice to the frigid Emperor Valluram&hellip;

&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t conceal yourself. Remove your hand, Princess Aleysha.&rdquo; Naked and exposed, Aleysha stands before the emperor and his icy stare&hellip;

Aleysha has lived in the countryside with her late mother all her life. One day, she is captured by the royal guards and learns her mother had stolen a jewel from the queen many years ago. To pay for her mother&rsquo;s crime, Aleysha is forced to wed Lynizen&rsquo;s Emperor Valluram &ndash; in hopes of gaining peace with the neighboring country. For the sake of unification, Aleysha will have to convince the emperor she&rsquo;s really a princess. However, she&rsquo;s at a loss when upon meeting Emperor Valluram, he rejects their arranged marriage &ndash; &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t need a sacrificial bride.&rdquo;

Cold and distant, Aleysha is wary of the emperor at first, but as she spends time with him, Aleysha sees he&rsquo;s more than he appears&hellip;and she finds herself drawn to his hidden gentle side&hellip;

[u][b]Chinese[/b][/u]
爱国爱民的掉包美乃滋王妃，因为恶毒的后妈，被送到隔壁国家的军装元帅皇帝那里用身体求和&hellip;&hellip;
